English: Enable 'Release Vassal' decisions
The Release Vassal decisions allow you to release vassals, and are otherwise kept hidden from view to avoid having them clutter up your decision list.
Disable 'Release Vassal' decisions
Your decision list will now be uncluttered!
Deactivate 'Release Vassal' decisions
The 'Release Vassal' decisions will disappear from this game session and won't reappear again. You won't be able to use these decisions again for this game.
